## Goal
Create comprehensive end-to-end tests for all filtering functionality to ensure filters work correctly, provide good UX feedback, and handle edge cases gracefully.

## Background
The application has multiple filter types (category, tags, search) that can be combined. Each filter change affects the prompt grid. Tests must verify:
- Individual filter functionality
- Combined filter behavior
- Clear/reset functionality  
- Accessibility of filter controls
- Mobile responsiveness
